high_descs: Move towards the toilet by the toilet paper roll holder
Pick up the grey spray bottle on the back of the toilet
Carry the spray and move to the grey trash bin to the left of the white door
Place the grey spray bottle inside of the trash bin

high_descs: Move forward, turn right and walk to the sink, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the gray spray bottle off of the toilet.
Turn around and walk toward the door, then turn left to face the chest of drawers.
Throw the grey spray bottle into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away the grey spray bottle that is sitting on the toilet.

high_descs: walk to the toilet ahead of you on the right
grab the spray bottle off of the toilet
turn left and walk over to the tub, then turn left and walk to the end of the room, then another left and face the bottom of the cabinet
place the spray bottle in the garbage bin to the left of the cabinet

high_descs: take a few steps forward and turn to the right and go to the wall and turn to the left and step to the toilet
pick up the spray bottle from the toilet tank

put the spray bottle in the waste basket

Put the spray bottle in the grey bin.
